net.minecraft.world.inventory.AbstractContainerMenu
net.multifusionlib.MultiFusionLib.screen.AbsMenu
public abstract class AbsMenu extends net.minecraft.world.inventory.AbstractContainerMenu
Abstract class representing a custom menu for a block entity. Handles the creation of slots for the player's inventory, hotbar, and the block entity's inventory.
